    "content": "Artist: Rihanna\r\nSong: Only Girl (in the world)\r\nTabber: Sleepy_Head\r\n\r\nThis tabs fairly simple, and has a few fills, but just listen to the song and \r\nthey'll be easy to get\r\n\r\nIntro\r\n----------\r\n\r\n[tab]G|---------|\r\nD|---------|\r\nA|---------|\r\nE|-2-2-2-2-| x8[/tab]\r\n\r\nVerse\r\n----------\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------|\r\nD|-----------------|\r\nA|-5-5-4-4---------|\r\nE|---------2-2-2-2-| x  (there are a few fills here, but i haven't worked them out)[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\nChorus\r\n----------\r\n\r\nPart 1\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----------------------------|\r\nD|----------------------------|\r\nA|------------------------5-5-|\r\nE|-3~-2-3-2-3-5---7-5-7-5-----| x2[/tab]\r\n\r\nPart 2\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------------------------------------|\r\nD|-------------------------------------|\r\nA|--------------------------------5555-|\r\nE|-3333333333322335555777777777777-----|[/tab]\r\n\r\nthen Chorus Ending\r\n \r\n[tab]G|--------------------------------|\r\nD|--------------------------------|\r\nA|--------------------------------|\r\nE|-333333333333333000002233333333-|[/tab]\r\n\r\nMain Chorus Part\r\n\r\n[tab]G|------------------------------------|\r\nD|------------------------------------|\r\nA|-------------------------------5-5--|\r\nE|-3-3-3-3-3-3-3-5-7-7-7-7-7-7-7------| \r\n   . . . . . . .   . . . . . . . . .[/tab]\r\n\r\n(i like to add a F# at the end of the first repeat, as it is a nice joining note) \r\n\r\nthen Chorus Ending\r\n\r\nRepeat Verse & Part 1 of Chorus & Main Chorus\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------|\r\nD|-----------------|\r\nA|-5-5-------------|\r\nE|-----5-5-7-7-7-7-| x8[/tab]\r\n\r\nRepat Main Chorus til finish\r\n\r\nhave fun\r\n\r\nPEACE :)",
